CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,FHe declared himself "back properly"
OL,7,Ffor the series decider at Trent
OL,8,FBridge, which starts on Thursday (25
OL,9,FJune), but declined the opportunity to
OL,10,Fsay he was back for good.
OL,12,F"I understand there's a lot of
OL,13,Fquestions that you (the media)
OL,14,Fprobably want to ask and want to hear
OL,15,Ffrom me, but I hope you respect in
OL,16,Fterms of this whole week, I'm (only)
OL,17,Ffocusing on this week," he said.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@cO]tD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,F"That's where my focus is at right
OL,7,Fnow. I understand there are probably
OL,8,Fsome questions but right now I'm here
OL,9,Fas captain of this team and all I want
OL,10,Fto do is get the team focused on
OL,11,Fwinning here. We are 1-1 in a three-
OL,12,Fmatch series and this week is massive
OL,13,Ffor the team."
