PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,FIn a subsequent interview with the
OL,7,FBBC's Test Match Special, Stokes
OL,8,Fadmitted the saga had forced him to
OL,9,Fponder whether he would be willing to
OL,10,Freturn to the ranks after four years
OL,11,Fleading the side.
OL,13,F"I'm 35 now and, even before this
OL,14,Fstuff all happened, I thought, 'Could
OL,15,FI ever see myself playing for England
OL,16,Fand not being captain?'. It's a
OL,17,Fquestion I've never really been able
OL,18,Fto answer," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,F"I love playing for England, I love
OL,7,Fbeing captain of this team and that's
OL,8,Fwhere I'm at with everything."
OL,10,FAsked if he had apologised to the team
OL,11,Fwhen he addressed them before training
OL,12,Fon Wednesday, Stokes said: "Of course.
OL,13,FThat was one of the things I had to do
OL,14,Fas captain.
OL,16,F"It's all fine, everything being fine
OL,17,Fand dandy, when it's going well but
OL,18,Fyou need to take responsibility for
OL,19,Fthings as well.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@^O]tD@\OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
