OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,F"You need to be big enough and man
OL,7,Fenough to be able to take that upon
OL,8,Fyour shoulders, look everyone in the
OL,9,Feye who it's affected and apologise
OL,10,Fhow you need to apologise. That's
OL,11,Fsomething I did."
OL,13,FStokes was guarded when it came to the
OL,14,Finvestigation itself, and did not
OL,15,Fweigh in on the disputed matter of the
OL,16,Fmidnight curfew.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
