PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,FHe did, though, speak up for his
OL,7,Frelationship with head coach Brendon
OL,8,FMcCullum. Suggestions of a growing
OL,9,Frift between the pair have been rife
OL,10,Fsince the Ashes defeat over the winter
OL,11,Fbut Stokes echoed the New Zealander in
OL,12,Fdefending their bond.
OL,14,F"It's been a big misconception around
OL,15,Fme and Brendon. We are genuinely very
OL,16,Fgood mates," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782328696
OL,3,CBen Stokes says he has apologised to
OL,4,CEngland team over night club incident
OL,6,F"We certainly haven't drifted apart,
OL,7,Fas there's a bit of speculation about.
OL,8,FNot agreeing on everything shouldn't
OL,9,Fbe seen as a divide between me and
OL,10,FBrendon. You are allowed to have
OL,11,Fdiscussions, you are allowed to have
OL,12,Fdisagreements.
OL,14,F"I feel like you need to get those
OL,15,Fthings out there with each other so
OL,16,Fyou can make good decisions. With me
OL,17,Fand Brendon, our relationship goes
OL,18,Fbeyond me being captain and him being
OL,19,Fcoach."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
